<plot>Hemel Pike is a canal barge casanova, aided and abetted by his illiterate cousin, Ronnie. Hemel has a girl in every town along his route, and each one is intent on marriage. He is finally caught when one of the girls, Christine, falls pregnant. Her protective father, a 'larger than life' character, who holds the canal record for drinking 29 pints of 'Brown &amp; Mild' in a single session, is understandably upset by his daughter's situation...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?542039</url></doc>
